t adthrive-content-13 adthrive-ad-cls" style=3D"min-height: 250px;"></div><=
h2><span class=3D"mw-headline" id=3D"In_spin-off_games">In spin-off games</=
span></h2>
<h3><span id=3D"Pok.C3.A9mon_GO_2"></span><span class=3D"mw-headline" id=3D=
"Pok=C3=A9mon_GO_2">Pok=C3=A9mon GO</span></h3>
<figure class=3D"mw-halign-right" typeof=3D"mw:File/Thumb"><a href=3D"https=
://bulbapedia.bulbagarden.net/wiki/File:Appraisal_GO.png" class=3D"mw-file-=
description"><img src=3D"https://archives.bulbagarden.net/media/upload/thum=
b/0/0d/Appraisal_GO.png/200px-Appraisal_GO.png" decoding=3D"async" loading=
=3D"lazy" width=3D"200" height=3D"347" class=3D"mw-file-element" data-file-=
width=3D"480" data-file-height=3D"833"></a><figcaption>Appraisal screen in =
Pok=C3=A9mon GO since version 0.149.0</figcaption></figure>
<p>In Pok=C3=A9mon GO, IVs have a range of 0 to 15. Pok=C3=A9mon have an IV=
 for each of their three base stats: HP, Attack, and Defense. With the abse=
nce of other mechanics such as <a href=3D"https://bulbapedia.bulbagarden.ne=
t/wiki/Nature" title=3D"Nature">Nature</a> and <a href=3D"https://bulbapedi=
a.bulbagarden.net/wiki/Effort_values" title=3D"Effort values">EVs</a>, IVs =
are the only factor that can distinguish one Pok=C3=A9mon's <a href=3D"http=
s://bulbapedia.bulbagarden.net/wiki/Stat_(GO)" title=3D"Stat (GO)">stats</a=
> from another's of the same species and form at each <a href=3D"https://bu=
lbapedia.bulbagarden.net/wiki/Power_up" title=3D"Power up">power up</a> lev=
el. A Pok=C3=A9mon's IVs can be evaluated using the <a href=3D"https://bulb=
apedia.bulbagarden.net/wiki/Stats_judge#In_Pok%C3%A9mon_GO" title=3D"Stats =
judge">appraisal</a> option on the Pok=C3=A9mon screen, which will display =
a bar chart indicating the IV for each of the three stats and a sticker tha=
t rates its IV total.
</p><p>If a Pok=C3=A9mon is <a href=3D"https://bulbapedia.bulbagarden.net/w=
iki/Trade" title=3D"Trade">traded</a>, its IVs will be randomly redetermine=
d, with possible values depending on <a href=3D"https://bulbapedia.bulbagar=
den.net/wiki/Friends_(GO)" title=3D"Friends (GO)">Friendship level</a>. If =
a <a href=3D"https://bulbapedia.bulbagarden.net/wiki/Shadow_Pok%C3%A9mon_(G=
O)" title=3D"Shadow Pok=C3=A9mon (GO)">Shadow Pok=C3=A9mon</a> is purified,=
 the IVs for all its stats are increased by 2. Pok=C3=A9mon can undergo <a =
href=3D"https://bulbapedia.bulbagarden.net/wiki/Hyper_Training#Pok%C3%A9mon=
_GO" title=3D"Hyper Training">Hyper Training</a> to increase their IVs, but=
 trading a Hyper Trained Pok=C3=A9mon will still randomly redetermine its r=
esulting IVs.
</p><p><a href=3D"https://bulbapedia.bulbagarden.net/wiki/Tyrogue_(Pok%C3%A=
9mon)" title=3D"Tyrogue (Pok=C3=A9mon)">Tyrogue</a> <a href=3D"https://bulb=
apedia.bulbagarden.net/wiki/Evolution" title=3D"Evolution">evolves</a> base=
d on its highest IV (chosen at random from all of its highest IVs if there =
is a tie).
</p>
<ul><li>Attack =E2=86=92 <a href=3D"https://bulbapedia.bulbagarden.net/wiki=
/Hitmonlee_(Pok%C3%A9mon)" title=3D"Hitmonlee (Pok=C3=A9mon)">Hitmonlee</a>=
</li>
<li>Defense =E2=86=92 <a href=3D"https://bulbapedia.bulbagarden.net/wiki/Hi=
tmonchan_(Pok%C3%A9mon)" title=3D"Hitmonchan (Pok=C3=A9mon)">Hitmonchan</a>=
</li>
<li>HP =E2=86=92 <a href=3D"https://bulbapedia.bulbagarden.net/wiki/Hitmont=
op_(Pok%C3%A9mon)" title=3D"Hitmontop (Pok=C3=A9mon)">Hitmontop</a></li></u=
l>
<p>A Pok=C3=A9mon's IVs are randomly assigned and uniformly distributed, bu=
t with guaranteed minimum values for certain types of encounters. The follo=
wing shows the minimum IV guarantees for each of the listed encounters. Unl=
