h4><span class=3D"mw-headline" id=3D"Determination_of_stats_3">Determinatio=
n of stats</span></h4>
<p>IVs in Pok=C3=A9mon GO are simply added onto the <a href=3D"https://bulb=
apedia.bulbagarden.net/wiki/List_of_Pok%C3%A9mon_by_base_stats_in_Pok%C3%A9=
mon_GO" title=3D"List of Pok=C3=A9mon by base stats in Pok=C3=A9mon GO">bas=
e stat</a>, and then the sum is multiplied by the <a href=3D"https://bulbap=
edia.bulbagarden.net/wiki/Power_up#CP_multiplier" title=3D"Power up">CP mul=
tiplier</a>.=20
</p><p><math class=3D"mwe-math-element" xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Mat=
h/MathML"><mrow data-mjx-texclass=3D"ORD"><mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scr=
iptlevel=3D"0"><mi>S</mi><mi>t</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy=3D"fals=
e">=3D</mo><mo stretchy=3D"false">(</mo><mi>b</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>s</mi><mi>e=
</mi><mo stretchy=3D"false">+</mo><mi>I</mi><mi>V</mi><mo stretchy=3D"false=
">)</mo><mo stretchy=3D"false">=C3=97</mo><mi>c</mi><mi>p</mi><mi>M</mi><mi=
>u</mi><mi>l</mi><mi>t</mi></mstyle></mrow></math>
</p><p>If a Pok=C3=A9mon is transferred from Pok=C3=A9mon GO to <a href=3D"=
https://bulbapedia.bulbagarden.net/wiki/Pok%C3%A9mon:_Let%27s_Go,_Pikachu!_=
and_Let%27s_Go,_Eevee!" title=3D"Pok=C3=A9mon: Let's Go, Pikachu! and Let's=
 Go, Eevee!">Pok=C3=A9mon: Let's Go, Pikachu! and Let's Go, Eevee!</a> or <=
a href=3D"https://bulbapedia.bulbagarden.net/wiki/Pok%C3%A9mon_HOME" title=
=3D"Pok=C3=A9mon HOME">Pok=C3=A9mon HOME</a>, the IVs will be recalculated =
directly based on the IVs it had in Pok=C3=A9mon GO.=20
</p>
<ul><li>IV for HP will equal <math class=3D"mwe-math-element" xmlns=3D"http=
://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow data-mjx-texclass=3D"ORD"><mstyle dis=
playstyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0"><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy=3D"false">=C3=
=97</mo><mi>I</mi><msub><mi>V</mi><mrow data-mjx-texclass=3D"ORD"><mrow dat=
a-mjx-texclass=3D"ORD"><mi>H</mi><mi>P</mi></mrow></mrow></msub><mo stretch=
y=3D"false">+</mo><mn>1</mn></mstyle></mrow></math></li>
<li>IVs for Attack and Sp. Atk will both equal <math class=3D"mwe-math-elem=
